Strong performance at Smart Infrastructure and Mobility

Revenue at Digital Industries totaled €4.6 billion and remained nearly stable on a comparable basis. Higher revenue at the software business was more than offset by revenue declines at the automation businesses, particularly in the case of higher- margin products. Orders declined 31 percent on a comparable basis to €4.0 billion due primarily to the automation businesses as market conditions softened year- over-year and customers continued destocking. Profit declined 20 percent to